comment5.target=boolean\ isMovingForward()
comment5.text=\r\n\ Checks\ if\ the\ tank\ is\ moving\ forward.\r\n\ @return\ False,\ because\ this\ type\ of\ the\ tank\ is\ stationary.\r\n
